snippet.title: Hunter Hitman Walkthrough
snippet.description:
00:07 - Level 1 - 5
03:21 - Level 6 - 10
08:02 - Level 11 - 15
14:14 - Level 16 - 20
20:54 - Level 21 - 25
26:55 - Level 26 - 30
34:47 - Level 31 - 35
40:56 - Level 36 - 40
53:51 - Level 41 - 45
01:06:13 - Level 46 - 50
01:18:55 - Level 51 - 55
01:37:23 - Level 56 - 58
Hunter Hitman is an action game where you play as a hitman armed with just a knife and your skills in the assassination. Sneak up on your enemies and eliminate them all. Kill multiple targets in a short time, and you will get a combo. Earn coins and unlock cards to obtain different character skins. 
You can play the game:
https://www.crazygames.com/game/hunter-hitman
